comments: Reid (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in George's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Beverley (MIN) legally contests Jackson's (LAC) jump shot attempt.

After Russell (MIN) cleanly intercepts the pass, Batum (LAC) establishes himself in Russell's path and incidental contact occurs as they come together.  Batum reaches in after absorbing the contact and makes clean contact with the ball, but does not dislodge it from Russell's possession.
During the throw-in, Edwards (MIN) moves through Jackson's (LAC) legally obtained space and dislodges him from his defensive position.

After Jackson (LAC) deflects the rebound, marginal contact occurs when he and Beverley (MIN) come together.  Jackson then makes contact with his teammate Morris Sr. (LAC), causing him to lose his balance.
Jackson (LAC) deflects the loose ball out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Timberwolves.
Zubac (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Beverley's (MIN) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the screen.
Russell (MIN) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Russell (MIN) moves alongside George (LAC) while resting a hand to his front and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact.
George (LAC) legally contests Russell's (MIN) jump shot attempt.

Beverley (MIN) comes together with George (LAC) and incidental foot to foot contact occurs, which causes Beverley to lose his balance during the rebound. He then makes incidental contact with Morris Sr. (LAC) and his teammate Reid (MIN) as they also lose their balance.
Russell (MIN) commits a take foul on George (LAC).

McDaniels (MIN) jumps alongside of Jackson (LAC) and marginal contact occurs when he momentarily rests a hand on his body during the driving shot attempt. Vanderbilt (MIN) swipes down as he contests the shot but avoids making contact with Jackson.
Vanderbilt (MIN) cleanly deflects the rebound away from Zubac (LAC).
Zubac (LAC) brings his arm down and makes contact with Edwards' (MIN) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Vanderbilt (MIN) legally contests George's (LAC) jump shot attempt and any contact after the release is deemed marginal.
Jackson (LAC) and McDaniels (MIN) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound.
Morris Sr. (LAC) commits a take foul on Beverley (MIN).
Beverley (MIN) makes clean ball contact to dislodge it from Jackson (LAC) during the drive. Any follow-through contact after the ball is dislodged is deemed incidental.
Zubac (LAC) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
McDaniels (MIN) grazes George's (LAC) shoulder as he loses control of his dribble and the contact is marginal.
McDaniels (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Jackson's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Batum (LAC) commits a take foul on Beasley (MIN).
A delay of game violation is correctly whistled on the Timberwolves.
Edwards (MIN) makes clean ball contact with the ball during the rebound.
